# Research Data Landscape Analyzer - Environment Variables

# ============================================================================
# REQUIRED: Anthropic API (for AI evaluation of papers)
# ============================================================================
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: Paper Source API Keys
# ============================================================================
# These improve results but the tool will work without them (with reduced coverage)

# Papers with Code API
# Get your API key from: https://paperswithcode.com/api/v1/docs/
# Note: Without this key, Papers with Code scraper may return HTML instead of JSON
PAPERS_WITH_CODE_API_KEY=your-paperswithcode-api-key-here

# ============================================================================
# CONFIGURATION NOTES
# ============================================================================
#
# Source Status (as of configuration):
# - arXiv: No API key required, works out of box
# - Semantic Scholar: No API key required, works out of box
# - Papers with Code: API key recommended to avoid rate limiting/HTML responses
# - DBLP: No API key required, works out of box
# - OpenAlex: No API key required (uses email in polite API mode)
#
# For OpenAlex configuration, update config/sources.json with your email address
# in the "openalex.email" field (required by their polite API policy)
#
